{"tid":1269283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿戰須停火？中國債務急飆　窒礙放水救市","createTime":"2019-06-30T13:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:13:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25561f131e6c19d0221ba2e30d41a35a0fe781cc","tid":1269283,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"貿戰須停火？中國債務急飆 窒礙放水救市<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190619/bkn-20190619143321905-0619_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190619%2Fbkn-20190619143321905-0619_00842_001.html&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=b142413c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190619/bkn-20190619143321905-0619_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普經常強調中國必須達成貿易協議，或者以下是原因之一！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日本傳媒報道，截至今年3月底止，中國整體債務佔國內生產總值(GDP)比重達248.8%，較2018年底高5.1個百分點。隨着中美貿易戰持續升溫及中國經濟增長放緩，中國勢必推出更多刺激經濟措施，整體負債恐進一步上升，恐成為「計時炸彈」。</span><br />\n<br />\n報道指出，中國債務激增主因是今年首季銀行業放貸達6.3萬億元人民幣，為紀錄新高。中國社科院高級經濟學家張曉靜坦言，首季經濟表現不錯，但不是免費午餐，整體負債佔GDP比重增幅超乎預期。中國可能重返整體債務佔GDP比重每年雙位數增長，風險相當嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，對上一次中國整體債務佔GDP比重按季增幅超過5個百分點，已是2016年首季，當時正值市場憂慮中國經濟前景，令政府允許銀行業增加放貸救市。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由2012年起，中國整體債務佔GDP比重就以每年10％至20%的速度增加，直到2017年要求「去槓桿」，令2017年9月底以來，中國整體債務佔GDP比重處於245%左右。截至今年3月底止，企業整體負債佔GDP比重達156.9%，較去年底增加3.3個百分點，單是國有企業就佔其中的68%。</span>"},{"pid":"6fa0bd691c23b9cfd3fefc5ca0fca25b44b4f140","tid":1269283,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6290ed5c2f8056d2f461b66174a67baeed60e3","tid":1269283,"uid":22822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"燒山快D話支国唔會爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0503b4536439ec19553ace657f36ecce25145b7","tid":1269283,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"爆咗先再叫我起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f36a391c5b93be833dc0768f42fa7dae3e2a378","tid":1269283,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0503b4536439ec19553ace657f36ecce25145b7","tid":1269283,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"爆咗先再叫我起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n我覺得支國真係爆到盡香港先會有消息"},{"pid":"dc36cf6a7240c2d2c4c823638a8a48843dd0e5a6","tid":1269283,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"爆未呀仆街"},{"pid":"de5ae5d03d41e7c6aef16c1beca48fc9d4eafe85","tid":1269283,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"送緊啲人番鄉下創業啦<br />\n你話爆未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}